text: The Nine O'Clock News may refer to: * RTÉ News: Nine O'Clock (1961–present) * BBC Nine O'Clock News (1970–2000) * KBS Nine O'Clock News, also known as KBS News 9 (1973–present) * Not the Nine O'Clock News (1979–1982) * Not Necessarily the News, based on Not the Nine O'Clock News (1983–1990) ==See also== * One O'Clock News (disambiguation) * Five O'Clock News (disambiguation) * Six O'Clock News (disambiguation) * Ten O'Clock News (disambiguation)
title: Nine O'Clock News
